---
title: Sage and Browned Butter Pork Chops with Roasted Broccoli and Citrusy Potato Salad
description: This luxurious dinner is simple enough for any weeknight. Perfectly seared pork chops are topped with an herby brown butter sauce for an unbelievably juicy outcome. The crunch of a bright and lemony potato salad adds a welcome contrast and brings this dish over the top!
